FBIS4-24619 "drchi105_i_94006" FBIS-CHI-94-105 Daily Report 31 May 1994 East Europe Slovenian Deputy Prime Minister Arrives in Beijing Slovenian Deputy Prime Minister Arrives in Beijing OW3105142194 Beijing XINHUA in English 1347 GMT 31 May 94 OW3105142194 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 31 (XINHUA) -- Lojze Peterle, deputy prime minister and minister of foreign affairs of the Republic of Slovenia, arrived here by air this evening. Lojze Peterle has come for a six-day official visit to China as guest of his Chinese counterpart Qian Qichen . Chinese Vice-Foreign Minister Dai Bingguo and Slovenian Ambassador to China Ivan Senicar [name as received] were among those present at the airport to greet the Slovenian guests.
